ranean basin.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aEtruscansxAntiquities. 0aEtruscanszItalyzCetamura del Chianti Site. 0aExcavations (Archaeology)zItalyzCerveteri. 0aExcavations (Archaeology)zItalyzCetamura del Chianti Site. 0aMaterial culturezItalyzCerveterixHistory. 0aRomanszItalyzCetamura del Chianti Site. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Archaeology.2bisacsh1 aAmbrosini, Laura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBellelli, Vincenzo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBonfante, Larissa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCamporeale, Giovannangelo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCausey, Faya, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCerasuolo, Orlando, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDe Puma, Richard Daniel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEdlund-Berry, Ingrid, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrummond, Nancy Thomson de, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHarari, Maurizio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLulof, Patricia S., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMichetti, Laura M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNagy, Helen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNaso, Alessandro, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPieraccini, Lisa C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPieraccini, Lisa, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRasmussen, Tom, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relato